metadata.name: NoSleep X DRES13- MARGE
metadata.description:
DRES13 is a web3 creative and visual artist known for his ongoing project, Marge: Assassin. It follows Marge Simpsonaru, a sword-wielding assassin seeking revenge for her family, in the deadly streets of Springjuku. DRES13's 1/1 and edition artworks showcase the world of Springjuku and its fierce protagonist.

Artist intro: Andr√© Greppi aka DRES13 is a visual artist, designer, and associate creative director working in web3 and his personal project- Marge: Assassin

Exhibition: In an alternate reality, Marge Simpsonaru is a sword-wielding assassin on a blood-soaked mission to avenge her family. leaves a trail of bodies as she cuts her way through the deadly streets of Springjuku. MARGE: Assassin is an ongoing collection of 1/1 and edition artworks created by DRES13, featuring the world of Springjuku and our favorite blue-haired femme fatale.
